<p>You probably build websites and think your stuff is so cool. You think your 13 megabyte parallax-ative home page is going to get you some Awwward banner you can glue to the top corner of your site. You think your 40-pound jQuery file and 83 polyfills give IE7 a thrill because it finally has box-shadow. Wrong, sweetie. Let me describe your perfect-ass website:</p>
